<img src="http://c.biz-file.com/c/1804/436721.jpg?2" alt="#OneShow2018: Responsive Environment finalists revealed!" width="625" height="325">This year’s ‘responsive environments’ categories include; architecture enhancement, user activation, use of technology, use of technology – augmented reality (AR), use of technology – integration with social platforms, craft – dynamic data visualisation and innovation in responsive environments.Click here for the full list of finalists, which includes all the gold, silver and bronze pencils as well as merit winners. The winners and full award details will be announced during One Show Creative Week in New York, from 7 to 11 May.You can view these and other One Show entries by browsing this year’s finalist showcase. Visit our One Show special section for all the latest updates!